---
const techStack = ["Python", ".NET Core", "Java", "Machine Learning", "AI/LLMs", "Data Analysis"];
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-gray-800 bg-gray-900/30">
	<div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">
			About
		</h2>

		<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-12">
			<p>
				I'm a Generative AI Specialist and Data Scientist with extensive experience
				building intelligent solutions that solve real-world problems.
			</p>

			<p>
				With many years as a software developer, I bring a strong technical foundation
				that allows me to bridge the gap between cutting-edge AI research and practical,
				production-ready applications.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div>
			<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Technologies</h3>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
				{techStack.map(tech => (
					<span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-800 text-emerald-400 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium border border-gray-700">
						{tech}
					</span>
				))}
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
